webResources.textAttributionSnippet:
(en) Aerial view of Falerum 1933. At the time of the picture, the resort still belonged to Småland (transferred to Östergötland 1971). The foreground sees Mariedal’s use. View to the South. 
Note: The injury in the lower corner appears to be a conscious retouch of the postcard producer - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMFA000036. AB Flygtrafik. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021016419428. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
